Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.consume

Provides interfaces and classes for consuming WSDL message data by BPEL activities and other supporting objects (e.g., invoke activity, receive activity, and onEvent element of a pick activity).

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeMessageDataConsumer Defines interface for consuming incoming message data.
IAeMessageDataConsumerContext Defines the interface for a message data consumer to interact with a BPEL implementation object.
 

Class Summary
AeAbstractMessageDataConsumer The base class for message data consumers that provides access to a delegate IAeMessageDataConsumerContext.
AeActivityInvokeConsumerContext Implements access to an invoke activity for a message data consumer.
AeActivityReceiveConsumerContext Implements access to a receive activity for a message data consumer.
AeFromPartsMessageDataConsumer Implements a message data consumer that copies data according to a series of fromPart definitions.
AeNoopMessageDataConsumer Implements a message data consumer that does nothing.
AeOnMessageConsumerContext Implements access to an onMessage implementation object for a message data consumer.
AeVariableMessageDataConsumer Implements a message data producer that copies data to a variable.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.consume Description

Provides interfaces and classes for consuming WSDL message data by BPEL activities and other supporting objects (e.g., invoke activity, receive activity, and onEvent element of a pick activity).
